edu.rit.classfile - package edu.rit.classfile
Package edu.rit.classfile is the RIT Classfile Library for analyzing and synthesizing class files.
edu.rit.classfile.unittest - package edu.rit.classfile.unittest
Package edu.rit.classfile.unittest contains unit test programs that demonstrate how to use the RIT Classfile Library.
edu.rit.m2mi - package edu.rit.m2mi
Package edu.rit.m2mi is the API for Many-to-Many Invocation (M2MI).
edu.rit.m2mi.life3 - package edu.rit.m2mi.life3
Package edu.rit.m2mi.life3 is a program for John Horton Conway's Game of Life using M2MI.
edu.rit.m2mi.matrix1 - package edu.rit.m2mi.matrix1
Package edu.rit.m2mi.matrix1 is a program for computing a matrix product using M2MI with omnihandles.
edu.rit.m2mi.matrix2 - package edu.rit.m2mi.matrix2
Package edu.rit.m2mi.matrix2 is a program for computing a matrix product using M2MI with multihandles.
edu.rit.m2mi.nbodies1 - package edu.rit.m2mi.nbodies1
Package edu.rit.m2mi.nbodies1 is a program for the N Bodies Problem using M2MI.
edu.rit.m2mi.test - package edu.rit.m2mi.test
Package edu.rit.m2mi.test contains test and demonstration programs for distributed applications based on Many-to-Many Invocation (M2MI).
edu.rit.m2mp - package edu.rit.m2mp
The M2MP API is a prototype class library implementing the Many-to-Many Protocol (M2MP).
edu.rit.m2mp.debug - package edu.rit.m2mp.debug
Package edu.rit.m2mp.debug contains channels useful for debugging an M2MP application.
edu.rit.m2mp.ip - package edu.rit.m2mp.ip
Package edu.rit.m2mp.ip contains Many-to-Many Protocol (M2MP) channel implementations that use UDP datagrams to convey M2MP packets.
edu.rit.m2mp.packet - package edu.rit.m2mp.packet
Package edu.rit.m2mp.packet contains classes that encapsulate the packets in the Many-to-Many Protocol (M2MP).
edu.rit.m2mp.test - package edu.rit.m2mp.test
Package edu.rit.m2mp.test contains test programs for the M2MP API.
edu.rit.util - package edu.rit.util
Package edu.rit.util contains general utility components.
